title: I'm a full stack developer based in Europe.
description: Hi, my name is Johnny Aguilera. Nice to e-meet you here. This section will help you know a bit more about me.
description2: I have mainly been involved in both front and back end sides of web projects during my career. Creating new projects from scratch or migrating old projects to newer and more perfomant version using new technologies. I try to keep learning every day something new, this is the most exciting about web and software engineering. Its evolution is happening fast and it is challenging to stay up to date.
